column5: Well i promised myself when i joined this forum back in 2008 that i would get at least one fishing report in before my 5th year anniversary. As most of you know. Im a shy person and a man of few words so ill just let the pictures do the talking ...how the time flies when your having fun    Ill start working on the next report in Novemberish of 2018,,, May we all find ourselves happy healthy and not on mod Q at that time  Cheers
Very impressive, and I don't get impressed easily. Worth many thousand stories.
I dont get the disco ball of difficult to view pics, but great fish. Thanks for the report.
Looks like you had a ball the last 5 years. Thanks for the report.
